<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>ANAS DENIM JEANS</title>

<style>
*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
    font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
}

body{
    background:#f4f4f4;
    color:#333;
}

header{
    background:#111;
    color:#fff;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:space-between;
    align-items:center;
    padding:20px 60px;
    position:sticky;
    top:0;
}

header h1{
    color:#3fa9f5;
}

nav a{
    color:white;
    text-decoration:none;
    margin-left:20px;
    transition:.3s;
}

nav a:hover{
    color:#3fa9f5;
}

.hero{
    background:linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,.6),rgba(0,0,0,.6)),
    url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1541099649105-f69ad21f3246?w=1400");
    background-size:cover;
    background-position:center;
    height:500px;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:center;
    align-items:center;
    text-align:center;
    color:white;
}

.hero h2{
    font-size:55px;
}

.hero p{
    margin:20px 0;
    font-size:20px;
}

.btn{
    background:#3fa9f5;
    color:white;
    padding:15px 35px;
    text-decoration:none;
    border-radius:5px;
    display:inline-block;
}

.btn:hover{
    background:#111;
}

.products{
    padding:60px;
    text-align:center;
}

.products h2{
    margin-bottom:40px;
}

.grid{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr));
    gap:25px;
}

.card{
    background:white;
    border-radius:10px;
    overflow:hidden;
    box-shadow:0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.15);
    transition:.4s;
}

.card:hover{
    transform:translateY(-10px);
}

.card img{
    width:100%;
    height:300px;
    object-fit:cover;
}

.card h3{
    margin:15px;
}

.price{
    color:red;
    font-size:22px;
    font-weight:bold;
}

button{
    background:#111;
    color:white;
    border:none;
    padding:12px 25px;
    margin:20px;
    cursor:pointer;
    border-radius:5px;
}

button:hover{
    background:#3fa9f5;
}

.about{
    background:white;
    padding:70px;
    text-align:center;
}

.features{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(200px,1fr));
    gap:20px;
    margin-top:40px;
}

.box{
    background:#111;
    color:white;
    padding:30px;
    border-radius:10px;
}

.contact{
    padding:60px;
    text-align:center;
}

input,textarea{
    width:80%;
    padding:12px;
    margin:10px;
}

footer{
    background:#111;
    color:white;
    text-align:center;
    padding:25px;
}
</style>

</head>
<body>

<header>
<h1>ANAS DENIM JEANS</h1>

<nav>
<a href="#">Home</a>
<a href="#">Products</a>
<a href="#">About</a>
<a href="#">Contact</a>
</nav>
</header>

<section class="hero">
<div>
<h2>Premium Denim Collection</h2>
<p>Comfort • Style • Quality</p>
<a href="#" class="btn">Shop Now</a>
</div>
</section>

<section class="products">
<h2>Featured Jeans</h2>

<div class="grid">

<div class="card">
<img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x300?text=Jeans+1">
<h3>Blue Slim Fit</h3>
<p class="price">$45</p>
<button>Buy Now</button>
</div>

<div class="card">
<img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x300?text=Jeans+2">
<h3>Black Denim</h3>
<p class="price">$50</p>
<button>Buy Now</button>
</div>

<div class="card">
<img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x300?text=Jeans+3">
<h3>Classic Blue</h3>
<p class="price">$40</p>
<button>Buy Now</button>
</div>

<div class="card">
<img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x300?text=Jeans+4">
<h3>Regular Fit</h3>
<p class="price">$42</p>
<button>Buy Now</button>
</div>

</div>
</section>

<section class="about">
<h2>About ANAS DENIM JEANS</h2>

<p>
At ANAS DENIM JEANS, we believe that denim should combine style,
comfort, and durability. Our collection is designed for everyday wear
with premium-quality fabrics and modern designs.
</p>

<div class="features">

<div class="box">
<h3>Premium Quality</h3>
<p>High-quality denim fabrics.</p>
</div>

<div class="box">
<h3>Affordable Prices</h3>
<p>Fashion that fits your budget.</p>
</div>

<div class="box">
<h3>Fast Delivery</h3>
<p>Quick and secure shipping.</p>
</div>

<div class="box">
<h3>24/7 Support</h3>
<p>We're always here to help.</p>
</div>

</div>
</section>

<section class="contact">

<h2>Contact Us</h2>

<input type="text" placeholder="Your Name"><br>

<input type="email" placeholder="Your Email"><br>

<textarea rows="6" placeholder="Your Message"></textarea><br>

<button>Send Message</button>

</section>

<footer>

<h3>ANAS DENIM JEANS</h3>

<p>Style • Comfort • Confidence</p>

<p>© 2026 All Rights Reserved.</p>

</footer>

</body>
</html>
